Text:  HMS S1 was a British submarine built in 1914 based on an Italian design. While on patrol on June 1915 the submarine’s engines failed. Text:  Rico Town Hall or Rico City Hall is a multi-purpose building in the tiny mountain mining town of Rico Colorado USA. Rico was formerly the county seat of Dolores County and the city hall was built as the Dolores County Courthouse in 1892 by a Mr. Carpenter.
